snippet.title: Shall we date?: Destiny Ninja ~Mizuki~ Changed Princess (Event Story)
snippet.description:
Shall we date?: Destiny Ninja ~Mizuki~ Changed Princess (Event Story)

This is Mizuki's Changed Princess event version. This is not the spin-off. Hope you like the story.  
I must warn that these are quite mature but is at your own risk.
Enjoy your romance!
